00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,200
he needs to be warned.

284
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,679
Isn't Shangshan Hu the Beiqi War God?

285
00:16:13,279 --> 00:16:15,279
He's good at fighting battles indeed.

286
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,360
But that may not be a good thing.

287
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,480
Your Excellency Fan, to be honest,

288
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:23,159
Shangshan Hu is transferred
back to Shangjing.

289
00:16:23,679 --> 00:16:25,200
Nominally, he is the Grand General,

290
00:16:25,679 --> 00:16:28,360
but actually he's only got
one hundred private soldiers by his side.

291
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,279
A promotion nominally
but a demotion in fact,

292
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,279
he has lost the military power.

293
00:16:34,639 --> 00:16:35,240
Indeed.

294
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,799
But he is to blame

295
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,799
for not understanding the situation.

296
00:16:42,639 --> 00:16:45,559
In such a complicated situation,
he neither pledges allegiance to His Majesty

297
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:47,200
nor visits the Empress Dowager.

298
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,840
As officials,

299
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,360
if you're not loyal,

300
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,000
what can you get? Right?

301
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,480
Then whose side are you on?

302
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,759
I'm loyal to the Empress Dowager.

303
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,279
Your Excellency Shen,

304
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,319
you're really outspoken.

305
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:07,000
I admire scholars

306
00:17:07,759 --> 00:17:09,240
all the time.

307
00:17:10,359 --> 00:17:12,000
Your Excellency Fan,
talented as you are in poetry,

308
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,559
have you written
any masterpiece recently?

309
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,480
Well, have you figured out

310
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:18,799
the secret?

311
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:28,279
He refuses to talk. No hurry.

312
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,400
There's still a long time ahead.

313
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,680
You've made

314
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,759
Xiao En suffer.

315
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,480
If he stages a comeback

316
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,839
in future,

317
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,680
he surely will get back at you.

318
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,720
Chen Pingping is worried, right?

319
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,319
When you're back, tell Head Chen that

320
00:17:52,039 --> 00:17:54,279
Xiao En has no chance.

321
00:17:55,119 --> 00:17:55,720
Just think about it.

322
00:17:56,599 --> 00:17:57,240
Even now, there's an assassin

323
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,200
trying to kill him.

324
00:18:00,119 --> 00:18:01,440
Many people want him dead in Beiqi.

325
00:18:01,759 --> 00:18:03,039
The number is no less than
that of Nanqing.

326
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,839
Well then, I will interrupt you no more.

327
00:18:10,799 --> 00:18:12,200
is arriving in Shangjing soon.

328
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:14,079
Just like I said,

329
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,160
man should understand the situation.

330
00:18:16,839 --> 00:18:17,359
Your Excellency Fan,

331
00:18:17,759 --> 00:18:18,640
don't make it hard for me.

332
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,839
Take your time and enjoy the food.

333
00:18:36,119 --> 00:18:37,000
Take them away.

334
00:18:53,079 --> 00:18:54,319
He serves the Empress Dowager.

335
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,000
So do you.

336
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,279
How come you two

337
00:18:58,279 --> 00:18:59,119
are fighting each other?

338
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,119
My teacher wants to kill Xiao En.

339
00:19:04,359 --> 00:19:06,000
As an apprentice,
I have to obey her order.

340
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:13,119
So I kind of saved your life.

341
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,480
You lifted the curtain just now.

342
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,880
I'm bluffing. Don't you understand?

343
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,400
What if your plan doesn't work

344
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,720
and he actually catches me?

345
00:19:21,039 --> 00:19:21,920
Then so be it.

346
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:22,960
How is that relevant to me?

347
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,799
Is it a joke for you?

348
00:19:27,279 --> 00:19:28,240
Will you assassinate Xiao En again?

349
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:31,640
I have no chance.

350
00:19:31,799 --> 00:19:33,759
After entering Shangjing,
I have no way to kill him.

351
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,279
Then when we reach Shangjing,

352
00:19:35,279 --> 00:19:36,079
let's cooperate with each other.

353
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:37,640
How?

354
00:19:37,839 --> 00:19:38,559
Anyway you like.

355
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,079
Whoever you find annoying,

356
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:41,119
I'll help you deal with him.

357
00:19:41,759 --> 00:19:43,079
By collaborating with me from within,

358
00:19:43,079 --> 00:19:44,079
we can bring trouble to the country.

359
00:19:44,839 --> 00:19:45,880
What's in it for you?

360
00:19:46,119 --> 00:19:47,240
I'm from Nanqing.

361
00:19:47,759 --> 00:19:48,839
The more chaotic Beiqi is,

362
00:19:48,839 --> 00:19:49,839
the happier I will be.

363
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,480
See you!

364
00:19:52,359 --> 00:19:53,359
Just think about it.

365
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,279
She's gone?

366
00:20:06,799 --> 00:20:07,519
Really?

367
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:12,440
She's gone.

368
00:20:14,839 --> 00:20:16,680
It seems that Beiqi is really chaotic.

369
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,799
This might be our chance.

370
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,720
Right,

371
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:22,880
we can seize the chance
to take the Saintess back.

372
00:20:23,279 --> 00:20:24,200
What're you thinking?

373
00:20:25,039 --> 00:20:26,920
It's our chance
to fulfill the mission task.

374
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:28,279
Right! Right! Right!

375
00:20:28,799 --> 00:20:31,279
It's a good excuse to fool the public.

376
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:33,920
Right!

377
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,319
Lend me some money.

378
00:20:35,799 --> 00:20:37,319
Give me silver instead of bank notes.

379
00:20:43,359 --> 00:20:44,960
I'll pay you twice as much
when we go back to the capital city.

380
00:20:46,039 --> 00:20:46,640
Twice?

381
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,839
You two, turn around.

382
00:21:08,599 --> 00:21:09,200
What's up?

383
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:10,480
At dawn tomorrow,

384
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:11,720
you should leave on your own.

385
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,240
Don't let others see you.

386
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,680
Go south to Shangjing Town,

387
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,920
and find a Tiaowang Inn.

388
00:21:16,599 --> 00:21:18,119
Take the money, get yourself a room,

389
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:18,920
and stay there.

390
00:21:21,119 --> 00:21:22,319
Why should I listen to you?

391
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,319
Only by helping me complete
the task of the Investigator's Office

392
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,440
can you get your father out of the jail.

393
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,359
Your Excellency, as you commanded,

394
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,880
our agents watch the place closely

395
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,119
and see a man from the Nanqing mission

396
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:03,359
slip away secretly.

397
00:22:03,839 --> 00:22:05,279
Now he stays in
an inn south of Shangjing.

398
00:22:05,759 --> 00:22:06,359
Should we catch him?

399
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:07,559
Leave him alone.

400
00:22:08,519 --> 00:22:09,559
Let him stay there

401
00:22:09,839 --> 00:22:10,640
as if we don't know.

402
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:12,559
Let's see what His Excellency Fan

403
00:22:12,799 --> 00:22:14,319
will do next.

404
00:22:15,759 --> 00:22:16,160
Yes.

405
00:22:23,359 --> 00:22:25,960
Your Excellency,
we've arrived in Shangjing Town.

406
00:22:27,039 --> 00:22:28,039
After taking Yan Bingyun back,

407
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,279
we can go home.

408
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,400
I'm afraid it's not that simple.

409
00:22:31,759 --> 00:22:33,039
Your Excellency,
you feel something might go wrong.

410
00:22:39,279 --> 00:22:39,759
Look!

411
00:22:41,359 --> 00:22:41,960
Here comes trouble.

412
00:22:49,079 --> 00:22:50,359
Greetings to you, Grand General!

413
00:22:51,519 --> 00:22:52,960
Whatever it is,

414
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,000
just send me a message.

415
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,359
How come you're here in person?

416
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:57,079
I want to see him?

417
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,440
See whom?

418
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:00,640
My adoptive father.

419
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:03,000
Who's your adoptive father?

420
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,200
Xiao En?

421
00:23:07,559 --> 00:23:08,839
So Senior Xiao

422
00:23:08,839 --> 00:23:10,319
is actually your adoptive father.

423
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,359
It's true that man
from a military family

424
00:23:12,519 --> 00:23:13,359
is bound to be extraordinary.

425
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:14,799
Where is he?

426
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,160
He's here! He's here!

427
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,160
What happened?

428
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,920
I interrogated him
according to the imperial edict.

429
00:23:42,519 --> 00:23:43,640
in the capital recently?

430
00:23:44,599 --> 00:23:45,079
Exactly.

431
00:23:49,799 --> 00:23:50,720
Grand General, since he's your father,

432
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:53,079
you can have a closer look at him.

433
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:54,559
What a pity!

434
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,000
I broke his legs,

435
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,759
or you might see him

436
00:23:58,759 --> 00:24:00,200
stand up.

437
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:09,759
Grand General,
are you satisfied with what you see?

438
00:24:09,759 --> 00:24:10,559
Give him to me.

439
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:11,519
I'm afraid I can't.

440
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,279
How dare you defy my order?

441
00:24:15,119 --> 00:24:16,359
Grand General, you don't know.

442
00:24:17,359 --> 00:24:19,319
His Majesty and
the Empress Dowager of Beiqi

443
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:20,960
ordered me to lock Xiao En up

444
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:21,920
in the Division of
Embroidered Uniform Guards.

445
00:24:22,319 --> 00:24:23,559
I can't defy the imperial order.

446
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,720
Grand General,
what else can I do for you?

447
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:39,960
properly.

448
00:24:44,759 --> 00:24:45,839
good for you.

449
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,839
Grand General,
thank you for the compliment.

450
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,960
I'm just loyal to my country.

451
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:02,319
Your Excellency.

452
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:05,240
Shen Zhong is not good at
dealing with other officials.

453
00:25:06,839 --> 00:25:07,400
Right.

454
00:25:08,799 --> 00:25:10,759
He's vicious and cruel,

455
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,559
but he's too arrogant

456
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:13,839
to restrain himself.

457
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,559
It will definitely get him into trouble.

458
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:16,839
Exactly.

459
00:25:17,319 --> 00:25:18,480
Shangshan Hu almost

460
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,000
attacked him just now.

461
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,680
He did it on purpose.

462
00:25:23,319 --> 00:25:23,920
On purpose?

463
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:26,519
From breaking Xiao En's legs
on the border

464
00:25:27,039 --> 00:25:28,720
to torturing Xiao En cruelly
along the way,

465
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,640
he did all that to provoke Shangshan Hu.

466
00:25:31,079 --> 00:25:32,359
Make Shangshan Hu attack him?

467
00:25:33,559 --> 00:25:35,559
After all, Shangshan Hu
has brilliant achievements in war.

468
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:36,960
To punish him,

469
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:38,440
there should be a reason.

470
00:25:39,359 --> 00:25:41,920
By making him attack the mission,

471
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:45,079
Shangshan Hu can be accused of
defying the imperial edict.

472
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,279
I'm afraid he will also

473
00:25:46,279 --> 00:25:47,279
be accused of treason.

474
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,799
Who gave the order,

475
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:52,200
the Empress Dowager of Beiqi
or the little emperor?

476
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,319
Maybe both.

477
00:25:55,799 --> 00:25:56,599
I didn't expect Shangshan Hu

478
00:25:58,079 --> 00:26:00,400
to be so feared in Beiqi.

479
00:26:00,839 --> 00:26:01,799
It's a good thing.

480
00:26:02,839 --> 00:26:03,559
Really?

481
00:26:05,759 --> 00:26:06,359
Your Excellency Fan,

482
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,599
His Majesty is anxious to see you.

483
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,680
I'm sorry that

484
00:26:09,759 --> 00:26:10,680
you'll have to first meet His Majesty
in the imperial palace

485
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:11,920
and then go to your residence.

486
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:13,559
We can go inside now.

487
00:26:33,519 --> 00:26:35,000
Won't Miss Si Lili
go to the imperial palace?

488
00:26:35,359 --> 00:26:36,240
She has no status.

489
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,920
She should live outside the imperial palace
and wait for the chance.

490
00:26:39,079 --> 00:26:40,839
Are you familiar with Miss Lili?

491
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:42,599
I caught her.

492
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:46,799
Won't Xiao En's carriage
go inside the town?

493
00:26:47,839 --> 00:26:49,039
He will go inside from the West Gate.

494
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,839
You also see what happened just now.

495
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,680
We don't know what will happen

496
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:53,759
when we go inside.

497
00:26:58,279 --> 00:27:00,319
When two counties are at war,
no messengers shall be killed.

498
00:27:01,039 --> 00:27:02,559
Nanqing has won a landslide victory
this time.

499
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,960
When entering the town,

500
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,480
we certainly won't see people
welcoming us on both sides of the street,

501
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:10,440
but they can't go so far as
to throw rotten eggs at us.

502
00:27:13,279 --> 00:27:14,759
Get out of Beiqi!

503
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,960
No envoy from Nanqing is welcome!

504
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:19,240
You! Get off!

505
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,359
Nanqing dogs!

506
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:24,160
You're not welcome! You're not welcome!

507
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:26,640
Get out of Beiqi! Get off!

508
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:27,640
Throw at him!

509
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:29,799
Get off! Get off!

510
00:27:32,039 --> 00:27:33,880
Get off! Get off!

511
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:37,079
You're not welcome in Beiqi!

512
00:27:37,079 --> 00:27:37,960
There're vegetables and eggs

513
00:27:38,039 --> 00:27:39,160
enough for several meals.

514
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:40,079
Let's add dishes tonight.

515
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:41,599
Got it.

516
00:27:42,039 --> 00:27:43,160
Get off!

517
00:27:43,839 --> 00:27:45,279
Get off, Nanqing dogs!

518
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,599
You're not welcome!

519
00:27:46,599 --> 00:27:47,599
Get out of Beiqi.

520
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,599
Our people are concerned
about national affairs.

521
00:27:49,799 --> 00:27:51,240
Since we lost the battle,

522
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:52,359
they can't help feeling angry.

523
00:27:52,519 --> 00:27:53,839
I'm afraid they're not
all common people.

524
00:27:54,519 --> 00:27:56,359
You killed Cheng Jushu,

525
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,599
the martial arts master of Beiqi,
on the street.

526
00:27:58,920 --> 00:28:00,920
Men in the army and on the streets
who practice martial arts

527
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,680
want to learn from you.

528
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,000
They are not bound by rules.

529
00:28:05,359 --> 00:28:07,599
They might assassinate you
or make a sneak attack.

530
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:10,279
You'd better hide in the carriage.

531
00:28:11,079 --> 00:28:12,400
It won't take long.

532
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,839
The Embroidered Uniform Guards

533
00:28:14,839 --> 00:28:15,599
can't even keep their own capital
under control?

534
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,880
I'm really not competent enough.

535
00:28:18,279 --> 00:28:19,519
Sorry! Sorry!

536
00:28:20,039 --> 00:28:21,400
As the envoy of Nanqing,

537
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,759
if I hide in the carriage

538
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,079
on my way to the imperial palace,

539
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,240
I'm afraid I'll dishonor

540
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,279
my country completely.

541
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:29,640
If you don't hide,

542
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,279
with more rotten vegetables
and worn-out shoes coming,

543
00:28:31,279 --> 00:28:33,000
it's not so honorable, either.

544
00:28:33,559 --> 00:28:34,759
So I'll dishonor

545
00:28:34,759 --> 00:28:35,960
my country either way.

546
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:39,079
I just can't quell the public anger.

547
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:41,319
You're really good.

548
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,799
You misunderstood me.

549
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:45,640
Wait!

550
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:47,640
Gao!

551
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:52,960
There's a long roll of cloth
on the carriage

552
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,119
which carries cargoes.

553
00:28:54,279 --> 00:28:54,960
Bring it to me.

554
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:56,000
Yes, Your Excellency.

555
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:07,559
Your Excellency.

556
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,960
Wang, drive steadily.

557
00:29:14,079 --> 00:29:14,640
I got it.

558
00:29:41,039 --> 00:29:41,599
Everyone,

