to stay where they are.

604
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,720
Don't charge or retreat.

605
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:05,079
Then Beiqi will tremble with fear.

606
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,640
According to time,

607
00:32:11,079 --> 00:32:11,839
Fan Xian should have arrived

608
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:14,079
in the capital of Beiqi.

609
00:32:14,799 --> 00:32:16,519
He should if everything goes well.

610
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:20,640
Will he cause any trouble?

611
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:25,200
Your Majesty, are the frontier forces

612
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:26,839
pressing on to the border for Fan Xian?

613
00:32:30,119 --> 00:32:31,799
He's the envoy of Nanqing.

614
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,519
Even if he causes any trouble,

615
00:32:36,079 --> 00:32:38,640
there will be
millions of frontier soldiers backing him up.

616
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,960
Well done! Good work!

617
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:23,079
Your Excellency, do you want a try?

618
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,440
Whoever is shameless

619
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,039
can make a sneak attack.

620
00:33:29,039 --> 00:33:30,400
I'll take it.

621
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,799
Your Excellency, watch out!

622
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:51,880
He Daoren.

623
