Where are your manners?

634
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:48,400
Your Excellency Fan,

635
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:50,760
the imperial palace is right ahead.

636
00:34:51,519 --> 00:34:52,800
By making such provocation,

637
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,840
do you want to restart the war?

638
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,320
Let's go.

639
00:35:11,199 --> 00:35:12,519
I'm really scared.

640
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,559
Will anyone throw things at me again?

641
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,760
Your Excellency,

642
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,000
you may stay here for a moment.

643
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,639
I'll go ahead to get things ready.

644
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,760
Your Excellency, please go ahead.

645
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,519
Your Excellency,
have you reached the Ninth Dan?

646
00:35:32,199 --> 00:35:33,119
You are injured!

647
00:35:36,159 --> 00:35:36,679
I'm fine.

648
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,440
So you're close to the Ninth Dan!

649
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,800
I've been practicing
Overbearing Vitality Qi.

650
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,360
What a cool name!

651
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,920
It's special for its strong power.

652
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:49,519
By fighting with Shangshan Hu

653
00:35:49,519 --> 00:35:50,559
and Haitang Duoduo along the way,

654
00:35:50,719 --> 00:35:51,320
I've made a breakthrough.

655
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,559
Competing solely
on the strength of vitality Qi,

656
00:35:53,719 --> 00:35:54,639
I can fight
a Ninth Dan martial arts master.

657
00:35:55,159 --> 00:35:56,559
But I'm far behind
in terms of subtle control.

658
00:35:56,679 --> 00:35:57,960
Your Excellency, no wonder

659
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,599
you put the flag on the carriage roof.

660
00:36:01,599 --> 00:36:02,159
Why?

661
00:36:03,639 --> 00:36:04,559
I stood on the carriage roof

662
00:36:04,719 --> 00:36:06,320
to avoid bodily movements.

663
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,639
If He Daoren

664
00:36:07,639 --> 00:36:08,679
wanted to knock me down,

665
00:36:08,679 --> 00:36:09,800
he had to go up.

666
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:11,880
Competing solely
on the strength of vitality Qi,

667
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:13,280
it's to my advantage.

668
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:15,519
If He Daoren attacked me
with his sword again,

669
00:36:15,639 --> 00:36:16,440
I would have to step aside,

670
00:36:16,559 --> 00:36:17,480
or I would be severely injured.

671
00:36:18,199 --> 00:36:19,480
Then why did Shen Zhong

672
00:36:20,039 --> 00:36:21,599
stop him just now?

673
00:36:22,079 --> 00:36:23,280
I'm the envoy of Nanqing.

674
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:26,400
If anything bad happens to me,
there'll be a war.

675
00:36:27,159 --> 00:36:28,199
Now Beiqi can't afford

676
00:36:28,199 --> 00:36:28,840
another war.

677
00:36:29,679 --> 00:36:31,400
Shen Zhong uses Beiqi people
to humiliate me

678
00:36:31,920 --> 00:36:33,519
so as to undermine
the morale of our mission.

679
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,880
But he dares not

680
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:35,559
hurt me.

681
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:36,320
At least,

682
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:38,079
I can't be hurt under his protection.

683
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,320
So we're

684
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,280
in an invincible position.

685
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,400
On this occasion,

686
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:44,800
I'm afraid it might be difficult

687
00:36:45,239 --> 00:36:46,320
to fulfill our task this time.

688
00:37:10,239 --> 00:37:11,679
It's so big here.

689
00:37:18,199 --> 00:37:19,079
Well, guys,

690
00:37:20,159 --> 00:37:21,159
what do you think?

691
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:23,199
It's solemn and magnificent.

692
00:37:24,199 --> 00:37:26,440
Beiqi is the most orthodox
of all countries.

693
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,320
Young and superficial as Nanqing is,

694
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,639
you even copied our imperial palace.

695
00:37:31,679 --> 00:37:32,719
Though young and superficial,

696
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:33,679
we actually won the war.

697
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,119
Your Excellency,
you have a sharp tongue.

698
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,360
It's no worse than
your martial arts skills.

699
00:37:38,679 --> 00:37:40,079
Your Excellency,
I've learned that from you.

700
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:43,679
Let's go.

701
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,320
His Majesty is waiting for us.

702
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:48,679
Let's go.

703
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:56,480
Your Excellency.

704
00:37:58,079 --> 00:38:00,079
His Majesty only wants to see you.

705
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:05,800
Let's go.

706
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:12,679
The envoy of Nanqing is here.

707
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,400
Nanqing envoy Fan Xian

708
00:38:27,639 --> 00:38:29,599
pays respects to Your Majesty of Beiqi.

709
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,719
I hereby present the credentials

710
00:38:30,719 --> 00:38:32,679
personally drafted by
